title: Senate Democrats and Republicans call for investigation into killing of Alex Pretti
description: Sen. Tina Smith, D-Minn., accuses the federal government of a 'cover up,' and Sen. Thom Tillis, R-N.C., warns White House against attempts to "shut down an investigation."
